 <Paragraph>
 This sample demonstrates how to apply a predefined built-in and custom styles to a table in the Word document using Essential DocIO.
</Paragraph> 

<Paragraph> <Bold>Note:</Bold> Currently table style support is only available for Word 2007, Word 2010 format and Word 2013 documents. </Paragraph>

